STATE
v.
George O. FREEMAN. No. 475P07-2. Supreme Court of North Carolina. June 11, 2008. Catherine F. Jordan, Assistant Attorney General, Peter S. Gilchrist, III, District Attorney, or State of NC.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 14th day of May 2008 by Defendant for Petition for Writ of Discretionary Review in the Supreme Court of North Carolina:

"Motion Dismissed by order of the Court in conference this the 11th day of June 2008."
